# ── prepack-generated copies ────────────────────────────────────────────
# README.md + LICENSE live at repo ROOT; the `node/copy-docs` prepack
# script copies them into node/ before `npm pack` so the published
# tarball contains docs (was missing in 0.1.2 — caught 2026-05-27).
# Generated artifacts are gitignored so the working tree isn't
# duplicated and "edit-in-the-wrong-place" footguns are blocked at the
# git-add layer.
node/README.md
node/LICENSE
